<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>Raiders Academy</title>
</head>

<body class="bg-light">
    
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand fs-4" href="#">Raiders Academy</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNavAltMarkup"
                aria-controls="navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
                <div class="navbar-nav">
                    <a class="nav-link fs-3 active" aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
                    <a class="nav-link fs-3" href="/admin">Admin</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="card shadow-lg p-4 rounded-4" style="background-color: #e3f2fd;">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h1 class="text-center fs-2 mb-4">Bem-vindo à Raiders Academy</h1>
                <p class="lead fs-4 text-center">
                    O projeto visa o desenvolvimento de uma plataforma web de fórum interativo entre os estudantes. Com tópicos
                    separados por matérias do curso, proporcionando um ambiente focado e eficiente para cada disciplina, criando uma
                    comunidade de conhecimento compartilhado.
                </p>
                <p class="text-center">Crie perguntas sobre qualquer tópico da matéria e estimule a participação ativa dos estudantes!</p>
                
                <form action="/save" method="post" class="mt-4">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="nome" class="form-label">Nome</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="nome" name="nome" placeholder="Insira seu nome" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="email" class="form-label">E-mail:</label>
                        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Insira seu e-mail" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-end">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Cadastre-se</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>


</html>